author: valsdav
body:
The new folder Ele_PFID_dnn contains both the tensorflow model files (.pb) and the configs files for the Egamma PFid DNN. 
The .txt config files contain both the list of variables to be used for each model and their scaling configuration. 

This is related to the PR https://github.com/cms-sw/cmssw/pull/35403 for CMSSW_12_1_0.
title: Including files for egamma PFid DNN
